notes:
Donate your old devices to Books for America - a 501(c)(3) non-profit organization whose mission is to build and improve reading libraries in schools, shelters, and many other organizations. We'll sell the gadgets online to fund our literacy efforts and people will receive a great (and easy) tax deduction. Some of the phones will be given to organizations we work with which support abused women (or otherwise disadvantaged women or families).
